Author: Hyde and Co
Title: [ANN][ICO] ğŸš€ğŸš€ HYDE & CO : Let's beat the market together! ğŸš€ğŸš€
Body: Hello,  A Hedge fund is basically an investment pool where investors put money and let someone manage the pool for them, in exchange, the so called hedge fund manager charges a fee (between 20%-40%) over the profits and a fee to operate the fund (0-3%). Collective here means that everyone can invest in the fund, not only the top 1% or rich institutions, which by the way are the major clients of big hedge funds. Our idea here is to let the average investor have the opportunity to profit with very little, or rather, controlled risk. If you want to know more please do not hesitate in contacting us directly at https://hcoinvestments.com/contact/. Thanks!
